# Rico AI — Architecture Diagrams (Mermaid)

## 1. High-Level System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Clients["Client Surfaces"]
        TG[Telegram Bot]
        WEB[Web App<br/>Next.js 14]
        JF[Jotform<br/>Onboarding]
        GP[GitHub Pages<br/>Dashboard]
    end

    subgraph APIGateway["API Gateway Layer"]
        FA[FastAPI<br/>src/api/app.py]
        AUTH[JWT Auth<br/>bcrypt + httpOnly cookies]
        RL[Rate Limiting<br/>slowapi]
        CORS[CORS Middleware]
    end

    subgraph Conversational["Conversational Layer"]
        RC[src/rico_chat_api.py<br/>1,576 LOC]
        IC[Intent Classification]
        RI[Role Intelligence]
        NLU[NLU EN/AR/mixed]
        MEM[Memory Retrieval]
    end

    subgraph AgentBrain["Agent Brain"]
        RA[src/rico_agent.py]
        SC[Scoring Engine]
        DE[Decision Engine]
        TR[Tool Registry]
        SF[Safety Guardrails]
        RT[Agent Runtime<br/>src/agent/runtime.py]
    end

    subgraph Legacy["Legacy Pipeline"]
        JS[JobSpy Fetch]
        FI[Filter & Dedupe]
        LLM[HF + Keyword Scoring]
        DEC[Decision Engine V2]
        NOT[Telegram Notifications]
        GM[Gmail Sync]
        FB[Feedback Loop]
        DB[Dashboard Generator]
    end

    subgraph Data["Data & State"]
        NPG[(Neon PostgreSQL)]
        RDS[(Redis<br/>Optional)]
        JSON[JSON Fallback<br/>data/*.json]
    end

    TG -->|Webhook / API| FA
    WEB -->|REST + WebSocket| FA
    JF -->|POST /api/webhooks/jotform| FA
    FA --> AUTH
    AUTH --> RL
    RL --> RC
    RC --> IC & RI & NLU & MEM
    IC --> RA
    RA --> SC & DE & TR & SF
    TR --> RT
    RT -->|Bridge| Legacy
    JS --> FI --> LLM --> DEC --> NOT
    DEC --> GM & FB & DB
    RA --> NPG
    RT --> NPG
    Legacy --> NPG
    NPG -->|Cache| RDS
    NPG -.->|Fallback| JSON
```

## 2. Daily Pipeline Execution Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant GA as GitHub Actions
    participant RD as run_daily.py
    participant JS as job_sources.py
    participant FI as filter.py
    participant LS as llm_scorer.py
    participant DE as decision_engine.py
    participant TB as telegram_bot.py
    participant DB as Neon DB
    participant GM as gmail_importer.py
    participant FB as feedback_loop.py
    participant DH as dashboard.py

    GA->>RD: Trigger (08:00 + 18:00 UAE)
    RD->>DB: init_db()
    RD->>RD: build_orchestrator()
    RD->>JS: fetch_and_score()
    JS-->>RD: ~43 jobs
    RD->>FI: filter_new_jobs()
    FI-->>RD: deduplicated jobs
    RD->>LS: score_jobs_llm()
    LS-->>RD: HF + keyword scores
    RD->>DE: generate_decision_insights()
    DE-->>RD: probability scores
    RD->>TB: send_telegram_message()
    TB-->>RD: notification sent
    RD->>DB: persist_history()
    RD->>GM: sync_gmail()
    GM-->>RD: 22 emails classified
    RD->>FB: run_feedback_loop()
    FB-->>RD: learning signals
    RD->>DH: build_dashboard()
    DH-->>RD: dashboard.html
    RD->>GA: deploy to GitHub Pages
```

## 3. Chat Interaction Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant TE as Telegram/Web
    participant API as FastAPI Router
    participant RC as rico_chat_api.py
    participant IC as Intent Classifier
    participant PR as Profile Repo
    participant OA as OpenAI Agent
    participant RT as Agent Runtime
    participant TR as Tool Registry
    participant DB as Neon DB

    U->>TE: "Find HSE Manager jobs in Dubai"
    TE->>API: POST /api/v1/agent/chat
    API->>RC: process(message)
    RC->>IC: classify_intent()
    IC-->>RC: intent=search_jobs, entities={role, location}
    RC->>PR: get_profile(user_id)
    PR-->>RC: RicoProfile
    RC->>RC: _is_live_job_search_request()
    RC->>OA: generate_response()
    OA-->>RC: structured reply
    RC->>RT: handle_action(user_id, "search_jobs", ...)
    RT->>TR: execute tool
    TR-->>RT: job matches
    RT->>DB: log_action()
    RC-->>API: JSON response
    API-->>TE: job cards + explanations
    TE-->>U: "Found 5 matches..."
```

## 4. Data Model Overview

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS ||--o{ PROFILES : has
    USERS ||--o{ CHAT_HISTORY : sends
    USERS ||--o{ APPLICATIONS : tracks
    USERS ||--o{ LEARNING_SIGNALS : generates
    PROFILES ||--o{ JOBS : searches
    JOBS ||--o{ SCORES : has
    USERS ||--o{ ACTION_AUDIT_LOG : performs

    USERS {
        string email PK
        string password_hash
        string role
        datetime created_at
    }

    PROFILES {
        string user_id PK
        string name
        string email
        string telegram_username
        json target_roles
        float years_experience
        int salary_expectation_aed
        json preferred_cities
        json skills
        json deal_breakers
        json green_flags
        json red_flags
        string cv_filename
        string cv_status
        json settings
    }

    CHAT_HISTORY {
        int id PK
        string user_id FK
        string role
        text message
        datetime timestamp
    }

    JOBS {
        string id PK
        string title
        string company
        string location
        text description
        string url
        datetime fetched_at
    }

    SCORES {
        int id PK
        string job_id FK
        string user_id FK
        float hf_score
        float keyword_score
        float combined_score
        datetime scored_at
    }

    APPLICATIONS {
        int id PK
        string user_id FK
        string job_id FK
        string status
        text notes
        datetime applied_at
        datetime updated_at
    }

    LEARNING_SIGNALS {
        int id PK
        string user_id FK
        string job_id FK
        string signal_type
        float confidence
        datetime created_at
    }

    ACTION_AUDIT_LOG {
        string action_id PK
        string action_type
        string user_email FK
        string job_id
        string job_title
        string result_status
        int duration_ms
        string source
        datetime timestamp
    }
```

## 5. AI Provider Fallback Chain

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[User Request] --> B{OpenAI<br/>gpt-4.1-mini}
    B -->|Success| C[Return Response]
    B -->|Rate Limited / Error| D{DeepSeek<br/>deepseek-v4-flash}
    D -->|Success| C
    D -->|Rate Limited / Error| E{HuggingFace<br/>all-MiniLM-L6-v2}
    E -->|Success| C
    E -->|Unavailable| F[Keyword Fallback]
    F --> C
```

## 6. Onboarding State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Started: Jotform submitted
    Started --> ProfileCreated: Webhook processed
    ProfileCreated --> CVUploaded: CV attached
    ProfileCreated --> ManualEntry: No CV
    CVUploaded --> Extracting: Trigger CV parser
    Extracting --> Enriched: Skills extracted
    ManualEntry --> Enriched: Profile complete
    Enriched --> OnboardingComplete: All fields filled
    OnboardingComplete --> Active: First job search
    Active --> Learning: Action feedback
    Learning --> Active: Preferences updated
```

